So the lyrics are still a work in progress.&nbsp; They still need to be cleaned up a bit.&nbsp; Constructive suggestions welcome.<br /><br /><meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8" http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" /><title></title><meta content="OpenOffice.org 3.1  (Win32)" name="GENERATOR" /><style type="text/css">
	<!--
		@page { margin: 0.79in }
		P { margin-bottom: 0.08in }
	-->
	</style> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&ldquo;Priest&rdquo;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">TTTO: &ldquo;Creep&rdquo; by Radiohead</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">When we burst through the door</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">I saw to my surprise</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">A round limbless creature</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">With hundreds of eyes</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Float o'er a battalion</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Of orcs and undead</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Warrior preps his special</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">They all prep their specials</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">But I'm a priest</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">I'm the healer</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">What the hell am I doing here?</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">I don't belong here</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">The party's far too hurt</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">And I know we've lost control</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">When their necromancer</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Steals our Elf ranger's soul</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">In horror I notice</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">When I turn around</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Our paladin's entrails</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">OH GOD THOSE ARE ENTRAILS!</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">I'm just one priest</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">I can't heal them</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">I'm only a level 3</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">I'm out of my depth here</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">So I... So I..</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Flee!  Run away again</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Flee!  Run!</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">I run, run, run, run, run...</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">My cloth armor's full of holes</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">My heart's beating fast</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">If that is adventure</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Then to hell with adventure!</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">I'm a priest</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Won't leave my temple</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">If you have wounds to heal</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">You must make it back here</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Good luck getting back here...</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">&nbsp;</p>
